I invite you to join me on the quest to love women, despite how the odds have been stacked against us. This pursuit will ask you to sit in depths of your shadows and pour light all over pain that has sat untouched for years beyond the ones you’ve spent in this body. You will be urged to sit in the center of a circle shaped by the women who have hurt you and be overwhelmed with waves of compassion and forgiveness. As you strip yourself from the programming what you will uncover is that each layer dissolves in the face of the truth, in the face of love. Beneath it all you will find a freedom you’ve known before the years you’ve spent in this body. 🧚

***BOOKING UPDATE***
I have come to realize that booking 1 month at a time, is inconvenient for both YOU & ME. It has you fill out a form OFTEN with lower chances of getting in due to high volume of requests & low availability in a one month span. 
•
I have decided that I'm going to book through the end of 2023. 
•
I will be booking using the forms that were already submitted in September!! HOWEVER, if you did NOT fill out a form in September and would like to request for the potential of November & December, there is a request form linked in my bio, I will be reviewing these as well.
•
If you already submitted a form in September, please do NOT submit another form unless it is for a different tattoo.
•
I will do my best to finish the booking process over the next few weeks!!
•
THANK YOU for your continued interest in my work. It truly means the WORLD to me... you have no idea. I'm excited to get 3x as many of you actually scheduled!!!! 🥂✨

As an artist, unless you've created other streams of income, if we get injured or sick & can not tattoo, we don't make money. This can be a pretty scary thought. With that being said, I really wanted to do this give away in support of the boiii @zac_siravo while he works towards making a come back. To hear more about his diagnosis, please check out the video he put together (linked in my bio)

I will be giving away 2 free tattoos:
-2nd place will receive a tiny tat or script ($400 value)
-1st place will receive a tattoo 6in or less ($800-1200 value)

TO ENTER:
•$10 entries paid through my venmo @nizzybop (linked in my bio!!)
•Unlimited entries!! If entering more than once, PLEASE include them ALL in ONE payment (ex: 10 entries, one $100 payment)
•Please put your instagram @ in the payment description!!
•If you are not interested in a tattoo but still want to support, please put "no tattoo" as the description, or donate directly to the gofundme!! (linked in my bio)
•This is to be booked for December 2023

Winners will be chosen on Sunday, 10/29!!
